        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer838769965" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8810979240846114778">This was a real eye-opener for me, as I had only a sparse knowledge of the region and its politics and history. Tim Butcher leaves you in no doubt as to the harshness of life in Liberia and Sierra Leone, but does so with warmth and humour in the face of immense difficulty. An enlightening, rewarding book, with a serious message to impart.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

<tr class="no_border feedFooterReview" id="update_comment_stuff_Review838769965">
