<div id="review_2877086022" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2877086022" />
    <a title="Schalk" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/27913250-schalk"><img alt="Schalk" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1398617447p2/27913250.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2877086022?book_show_action=true">Jan 18, 2021</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Schalk" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Schalk" href="/user/show/27913250-schalk">Schalk</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Kindle Edition " href="/book/show/12250856-chasing-the-devil">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2877086022" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7983609105856203862">If you love adventure travel and history, you must read Tim Butcher&apos;s books. I thoroughly enjoyed this book about adventure travel in Liberia, as well as an excellent background on the history of Sierra Leone and Liberia and the English writer Graham Greene.</span>
  <span id="freeText7983609105856203862" style="display:none">If you love adventure travel and history, you must read Tim Butcher's books. I thoroughly enjoyed this book about adventure travel in Liberia, as well as an excellent background on the history of Sierra Leone and Liberia and the English writer Graham Greene.</span>
  <a data-text-id="7983609105856203862" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
